title: Single row drilling machine US-RB-73211B
title_uz: Yog'ochga bir qatorli teshik ochib berish uskunasi US-RB-73211B
short_description: This US-RB-73211B model single row drilling machine consumes 1.5 KW of power per hour and also operates at an air pressure of 0.6-0.8 MPa. The maximum cutting diameter of the equipment is 35 mm and the maximum cutting depth is 60 mm. The overall dimensions of the equipment are 1400 x 1300 x 1400 mm.
short_description_uz: Ushbu US-RB-73211B modeldagi yog'ochga bir qatorli teshik ochib berish uskunasi soatiga 1.5 KW quvvat sarflaydi, shuningdek, 0.6-0.8 mpa havo bosimida ishlaydi. Uskunaning yog'ochga maksimal teshik ochib berish diametri 35 mm hamda maksimal teshik ochib berish chuqurligi esa 60 mmni tashkil etadi. Uskunaning umumiy o'lchamlari esa 1400 x 1300 x 1400 mmni tashkil etadi.
short_description_ru: Эта однорядная сеялка модели US-RB-73211B потребляет 1,5 кВт электроэнергии в час и также работает при давлении воздуха 0,6 - 0,8 МПа. Максимальный диаметр резки оборудования составляет 35 мм, а максимальная глубина резки – 60 мм. Габаритные размеры оборудования составляют 1400 х 1300 х 1400 мм.
short_description_en: This US-RB-73211B model single row drilling machine consumes 1.5 KW of power per hour and also operates at an air pressure of 0.6-0.8 MPa. The maximum cutting diameter of the equipment is 35 mm and the maximum cutting depth is 60 mm. The overall dimensions of the equipment are 1400 x 1300 x 1400 mm.
long_description:
Single row drilling machine US-RB-73211B.

Technical parameters of the equipment:

  • Model: US-RB-73211B.
  • Max drill diameter: 35 mm.
  • Max drill depth: 60 mm.
  • Number of spindles: 21.
  • Spindle speed: 2800 r / min.
  • Motor power: 1.5 Kw.
  • Air pressure: 0.6 - 0.8 mpa.
  • Dimension: 1400 x 1300 x 1400 mm.
